A registered company in Israel offering same-day Bitcoin Buy/Sell services to the Israeli market. 

##Deposits

* Regular Wire transfer (same day for Bank Leumi clients)
* Fast Wire transfer, also known as העברת זה"ב

##Withdrawals

* Wire transfer

##History
The exchange was opened on March 2013 after a short period of Private Beta.

